"You'll stumble and stagger-"-Dagger

Dagger is a Tiefling working for Lord Fargus. He was first encountered in the Faylil Forest. He's short-spoken, brash, and not too sharp. He works alongside Shank, who acts as the brain to his brawns.

We don't know much of his past as of yet, but we do know he has been trained well in the art of combat. His fatal flaw is his intelligence or lack thereof; tricking the big oaf isn't a difficult task.

He loves Rhymes and attempts to get Shank to agree to introduce themselves with them to varying degrees of success. I will say while I don't care for him or his actions, I do feel rather bad when it comes to the treatment of his sunglasses. Poor fellow simply wants to look cool...ah well such is life.
